Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.78,0:33:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,产权线就在这条裂缝的正下方\N{\fnarial\fs12\}the property line is right down on this crack{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.24,0:33:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就站在这里\N{\fnarial\fs12\}And we would stand right here{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.63,0:33:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,并说服那些来堕胎诊所的妇女们\N{\fnarial\fs12\}and minister to the women that were going in this abortion clinic{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.67,0:33:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果越过这条线，我们就会被逮捕\N{\fnarial\fs12\}If we stepped over the line, we'd be arrested{\r}
