Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.56,0:33:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}救援行动组织动用了所有的资源{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}Operation Rescue has targeted Wichita with virtually all of its resources,{\r}
