Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.37,0:33:57.31,自定义,,0,0,0,,（多少孩子死在这里；\N堕胎是魔鬼的交易）
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.00,0:34:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,成千上万的人因为乔治•蒂勒而来到威奇托\N{\fnarial\fs12\}Thousands of people came to Wichita, and that's because of George Tiller{\r}
