Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.63,0:35:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这关乎女性在社会中的地位\N{\fnarial\fs12\}I think this really is about women's status in society,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.04,0:35:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,控制女性的行为，以及这种行为的限制\N{\fnarial\fs12\}controlling women's behavior and the limits of that behavior{\r}
