Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.93,0:35:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}比如宫内节育器或避孕药，我认为都该被禁止{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}such as the IUD or the pill, I believe should be banned{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.48,0:35:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}事实上，特里先生已经透露了{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}Mr. Terry has in fact revealed{\r}
