Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.77,0:35:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这种情绪和激情围绕着堕胎\N{\fnarial\fs12\}The emotion and the hot emotion is around abortion{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.49,0:36:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这是谋杀，菲尔，这是我们法律的目的{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}It's murder, Phil. That's what we have laws for{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.31,0:36:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,它引发了很多关于性的冲突，而且…\N{\fnarial\fs12\}It raises a lot of conflict around sexuality, and{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.33,0:36:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问，这是令人生畏的\N{\fnarial\fs12\}without any question, it's formidable{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.16,0:36:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}…必须由妇女和她的医生来做这个决定{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}…must be decided by the woman and her physician,{\r}
