Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.69,0:36:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但最终的决定必须是女性\N{\fnarial\fs12\}But the ultimate decider here must remain women{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.46,0:36:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们真正为之奋斗的目标\N{\fnarial\fs12\}And that's what we're really fighting for{\r}
