Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.44,0:36:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}那些实施堕胎的人会怎样？特里先生？{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}what happens to those who perform the abortion? Mr. Terry?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.96,0:36:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这么说吧，等这一切结束后，乔治•蒂勒医生会坐很久的牢{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}Let me say this. Dr. George Tiller's gonna do hard time when this is all over{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.52,0:36:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他是一个杀人狂，他是人类的敌人{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}He is a mass murderer. He is an enemy of humanity{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.82,0:36:42.24,自定义,,0,0,0,,（抗议者枪击医生）
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.12,0:36:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}堕胎斗争已经发生了激烈的转变{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}The abortion battle has taken a violent turn{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.42,0:36:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一连串的枪声…\N{\fnarial\fs12\}It was just one round after another...{\r}
