Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.93,0:37:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,然后一名医生和一名随行人员被杀\N{\fnarial\fs12\}Then a doctor and an escort were killed{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.50,0:37:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}两枚炸弹在亚特兰大的一家堕胎诊所引爆{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}Two bombs rocked an abortion clinic in Atlanta{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.05,0:37:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}每一家堕胎诊所都是那些参与者的潜在目标{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}Every abortion clinic is a potential target for those who would do this{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.41,0:37:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在那一刻，我认为，有一种引力从运动中产生\N{\fnarial\fs12\}And at that point, I think, there was a gravity that came out of the movement{\r}
