Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.53,0:37:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}乔治•蒂勒医生在堪萨斯州威奇托的教堂被枪杀{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}Dr. George Tiller was shot dead at his church in Wichita, Kansas{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.48,0:37:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一名男子在路德教堂冷血地枪杀了他\N{\fnarial\fs12\}A man shot him in the Lutheran church,in cold blood{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.25,0:37:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}嫌疑犯已被拘留，现在警方…{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}The suspect is in custody, and right now the police{\r}
