Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.79,0:37:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是太惊人了，真是太惊人了\N{\fnarial\fs12\}That's really astonishing. That's just astonishing{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.53,0:37:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}在你信仰的经历中{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}Did there come a point in time where your faith,{\r}
