Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.29,0:37:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}是的{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}Yes{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.19,0:38:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我一直在看700俱乐部{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}I had been watching The 700 Club regularly{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.90,0:38:06.40,自定义,,0,0,0,,700俱乐部网络传教片段
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.90,0:38:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}因为婴儿是按照全能的上帝的形象制造的{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}'Cause that baby is made in the image of God Almighty{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.26,0:38:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我独自呆在起居室里…{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}I was alone in my living room, and{\r}
