Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.57,0:38:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,宗教可以使人发疯，它真的可以\N{\fnarial\fs12\}Religion can make people crazy. It really can{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.12,0:38:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这可能是美妙的，但也可能是难以置信的不宽容\N{\fnarial\fs12\}And it can be wonderful, but it can also be just incredibly intolerant{\r}
