Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.14,0:52:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗•威利克是新右翼运动的主要战略家之一\N{\fnarial\fs12\}Paul Weyrich was one of the chief strategists of the New Right movement{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.81,0:52:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}涉及的问题是宗教自由问题{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}Questions involved are religious liberty questions{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.60,0:52:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这是一场宣称我们将通过偏见赢得总统选举的运动{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}It was a movement that said we are going to win the presidency through bigotry,{\r}
