Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.00,0:53:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,吸引宗教选民的民粹主义议题\N{\fnarial\fs12\}that would appeal more generally to religious voters{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.10,0:53:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他很精明地意识到\N{\fnarial\fs12\}And he was savvy enough to recognize that{\r}
