Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.11,0:53:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}亲家庭运动和美国人民并不想{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}The pro-family movement and the American people do not want{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.87,0:53:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}把妇女解放的意识形态强加给我们所有人{\i0}\N{\fnarial\fs12\}the women's lib ideology forced upon all the rest of us{\r}
